snippet: While acknowledging Wednesday that he may not win the presidency in the first round, Vladimir V. Putin said that a second round of voting would lead to political turbulence in Russia.
abstract: Russian Prime Min Vladimir V Putin acknowledges that he may not win the presidency in the first round of voting, though he also says that a second round of voting would lead to political turbulence.
lead_paragraph: While acknowledging Wednesday that he may not win the presidency in the first round, Vladimir V. Putin said that a second round of voting would lead to political turbulence in Russia.

headline.seo: Putin Concedes He May Not Win 1st Round of Russian Elections
headline.main: Putin Concedes He May Not Win in 1st Round
headline.print_headline: Russia: Putin Ready to Go 2 Rounds
